### Banking Transaction API - Sample Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ===== TRANSACTION ENDPOINTS =====

### Create a new transaction (Deposit)
### Note: Deposits only require toAccount (not fromAccount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a new transaction (Withdrawal)
### Note: Withdrawals only require fromAccount (not toAccount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### Create a new transaction (Transfer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 500.75,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### List all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### List transactions for specific account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### List transactions by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=deposit

### List transactions with date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

### List transactions with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer

### Get specific transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/1000

### ===== ACCOUNT ENDPOINTS =====

### Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get balance for different account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

### ===== SUMMARY ENDPOINT =====

### Get overall transaction summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary

### Get transaction summary for specific account
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary?accountId=ACC-12345

